HEADWORD: Cursor
<hw>Cur"sor</hw> <pr>(k?r"s?r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., a runner.
See <er>Cursitor</er>.]</ety> <def>Any part of a mathematical instrument
